---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';

const exactTitle = "送信完了 | リラガーデン(RelaGarden)";
---

<BaseLayout exactTitle={exactTitle}>
  <Header slot="header-slot" />

  <div class="thanks-container">
    <div class="thanks-card">
      <div class="icon-wrapper">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="check-icon">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="thanks-title">お問い合わせを受け付けました</h1>
      
      <div class="thanks-message">
        <p>この度はリラガーデンへお問い合わせいただき、<br class="pc-only">誠にありがとうございます。</p>
        <p>ご入力いただいたメールアドレス宛に、自動返信メールをお送りいたしました。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="next-step-box">
        <h2 class="next-step-title">今後の流れ</h2>
        <ul class="step-list">
          <li>
            <span class="step-num">1</span>
            <p>内容を確認し、担当者より<strong>2営業日以内</strong>にご連絡いたします。</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="step-num">2</span>
            <p>現地調査をご希望の場合は、日程の調整を行わせていただきます。</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="button-group">
        <a href="/" class="btn-primary">トップページへ戻る</a>
        <a href="/cases/" class="btn-secondary">施工事例を見る</a>
      </div>

      <p class="note">
        ※しばらく経ってもメールが届かない場合は、迷惑メールフォルダをご確認いただくか、お手数ですがお電話にてお問い合わせください。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .thanks-container {
    padding: 80px 24px;
    background-color: #f9faf7;
    min-height: 80vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Zen Maru Gothic', sans-serif;
  }

  .thanks-card {
    max-width: 640px;
    width: 100%;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-radius: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: #f0fdf4;
    color: #22c55e;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
  }

  .check-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; }

  .thanks-title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #1a202c;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .thanks-message {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .next-step-box {
    background: #f8fafc;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .next-step-title {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .step-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .step-num {
    background: #2e7d32;
    color: #fff;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .button-group {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-cols: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: #2e7d32;
    color: #fff !important;
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: #fff;
    color: #2e7d32 !important;
    border: 2px solid #2e7d32;
    padding: 16px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: #1b5e20; transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: #f0fdf4; transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #a0aec0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .thanks-card { padding: 40px 20px; }
    .thanks-title { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .button-group { grid-template-cols: 1fr; }
    .pc-only { display: none; }
  }
</style>